THE GAME
--------

  'Zeeconn' is a Workbench game where you have to link together
the maximum possible number of coloured tiles on each game board.
If there are tiles of the same colour that are linked together,
the better it is...

  To play, click on a coloured tile (or a small dot) that is
located diagonally between two other coloured tiles. A link will
be created between those tiles and if the tiles at the end of the
link are of the same colour, the link will be of that colour,
otherwise the link will be of a 'neutral' colour. The clicked tile
will be transformed into a small dot. That tile can still be
clicked on afterwards, but it will no longer be used as a coloured
tile. The coloured tiles cannot be clicked again, however, they
still can be linked to other coloured tiles.

  A game board is completed when it is no longer possible to make
any links.

  Have fun!

